Ticket Sales Closed. No winners.

This is not a meetup until somebody buys a raffle ticket and wins this once in a life time event!

Would you pay $10.00 for a chance to watch the Red Sox Game vs the Texas Rangers on Saturday, August 4 with 17 FRIENDS AND RED SOX NATIVES in a Citizens Bank Private Box  with complimentary refreshments and food?

Get Raffle tickets at www.community servings.org Go to the LifeSavor on-line auction

Raffle Tickets are $10.00 each while they last.

Drawing to be held at LifeSavor event on Thursday, May 31
